title:          NFT Commission Standard
description:    This standard defines an interface for NFT commision between the operator and the owner.
author:         Steve Huguenin <steve.huguenin-elie@protonmail.ch>
discussions-to:  https://ethereum-magicians.org/t/nft-commission-standard/8655
status:         Idea
